# Stock count display names (copy to vendors/.display-names)
#
# Shown in the stock count UI only. Backend still uses the real catalog name,
# item code, and .item-codes aliases for Macromatix.
#
# Format:  Catalog name OR item code  |  Plain English label
#
# Examples:
# Oil Frying Liquid | Oil
# 39520 | Beef cooked
# DRINK PEPSI MAX 600ML PET 24EA | Pepsi Max bottles
